_sText:
This is my first cs:s map, though I've been mapping for quite a while (Garrys Mod 10). It is mainly a Gun game map, but if your happy with fighting with pistols, it can be used for that too. 

Some features are:
Skybox
DEV Textures
Large tower
4 Bunkers with openable doors (To get into them go threw the hole on the roof!
and 2 .. well holes to shoot out of.


File size: 551kb!!


I may make a second version.

If you wish to edit PM/Email me at pieclock@yahoo.co.uk

Enjoy! ^^
